formation, such as ensuring the\nself-consistency of the energy balance and tracking the quantum information\ntransfer in the detector-field system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Jun 2019 02:25:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-02"}
