ganize the high-shear and low-shear trapping regimes on a $Pe-\\kappa$ plane,\nthereby highlighting the singular behavior of infinite-aspect-ratio swimmers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Jun 2019 06:58:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Jun 2019 07:23:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-27"}
