 them to the values observed in Raman scattering\nspectroscopy. We also discuss the possibility of a multiplicity of orders in\nthe PG phase and give an overview of the phase diagram.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Jun 2019 14:56:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Aug 2019 14:41:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 16 Dec 2019 18:03:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-17"}
